description:
Join Danielle Dufault as she examines the history of the  T. Rex, one of the coolest dinosaurs of all time, and how our understanding has changed. Through fossil evidence and  prehistoric illustrations, see the  evolution of the tyrant lizard king in pop culture and in science.  It's a beast of a story!
